{
  "id": "glitch-agent-deploy",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Manage deployments of the Glitch and Sentinel agents: check current ARNs, update cross-agent SSM parameters after a fresh deploy, trigger CDK stack deploys, and check CodeBuild status. Use when the user asks to deploy, redeploy, wire up ARNs, check deploy status, or after running agentcore deploy locally.",
